AC-130 is an arcade shooter game with old-school gameplay delivered in a modern style. You are a TV operator (gunner) aboard an AC-130 gunship, tasked with providing fire support to friendly troops on the ground. Inspired by the famous CoD 4 mission.

Written in 2010 as part of a C programming assignment at the Silesian University of Technology.
Migrated from Sourceforge SVN in August 2013.

Dependencies: SDL 1.2, GLEW, OpenGL
